{
  "stem": "3973.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Up to that time, I never had long pants.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She shaved my upper lip that got some fuzz on it to make sure this doesn't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I took off leaving them in the woods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, when I left, the idea was I am not going to see them again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I didn't care.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I have this change began to manifest itself in this way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I ran away from them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Strangely enough, when I left the woods and I walked down the streets in the village, I had sort of a rucksack with some piece of bread and cheese in it and a little bit of money.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I felt free.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was a strange sense of freedom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because the responsibility for them, it-- it was-- it weighed on me so heavy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I can not-- I do not want to be responsible for the lives of others.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't know at the time what it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This all came back later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But at that time, I felt free.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now, the way to go to Krakow was to stand on a busy corner and hail German trucks, who occasionally would stop and take people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And sometimes it took many hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I see the-- the boy, who was part of the peasant family we were in, was going down the street.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he saw me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he ran back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then a few minutes later, the old man where we lived wearing his Sunday suit, is going down-- he was going to go, obviously, to report me to the police.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
